FIREBASE:

1. create project on firebase console.

2. Connect the firebase project with you app.
 
	There are two different ways you can use Firebase in your projects [ FOR REACT NATIVE ]:

	- Using Firebase JS SDK [ works with expo go ]
		🔗️ https://docs.expo.dev/guides/using-firebase/#using-firebase-js-sdk
		
	- Using React Native Firebase [ works with react-native cli ]
		🔗️ https://docs.expo.dev/guides/using-firebase/#using-react-native-firebase
